   if ($textbook eq "EllisGulick5") {
BEGIN_TEXT
Note that this problem is similar to problems 7 and 10 of Section 5.2 in
the text, except you are asked to use midpoint sums instead of upper and
lower sums.
END_TEXT
}
}

